<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dy kẖṭẗ ḥyạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (dy kẖṭẗ ḥyạty .. ḍạmnhạ fy ạydyk
 sẖạyfhạ ywmạty .. gẖlạwty ʿlyk)2
 (ḥạsshạ fy ạ̉mạny .. slạmy wḍmạny
 fy kl ạlmʿạny .. ạlḥlwẗ ạlly fyk)2
 2- (fy ywm mạ thạjmny .. ryạḥ ạlḥyạẗ
 wbḍgẖṭ tlạkẖmny .. wmạfysẖ ṭwq njạh)2
 (ạ̉sẖwfk qryb .. ḥnyn wṭyb
 wkẖạṭry tṭyb .. yạ ạ̉rwʿ ạ̹lh)2
 3- (mạ fy sẖyʾ yhdd .. sẖʿbk fy ạlmrạʿy
 wlạ sẖyʾ ybdd .. kẖrạfk yạ rạʿy)2
 (syj ḥwạlyã .. wwʿdk dạ lyã
 ạ̹ny jwh fy ydk .. qlby wsẖrạʿy)2</lyrics>
